      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p>Your nanites form an enhancing lattice in your brain, making you capable of mental leaps of staggering brilliance. When you use the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.0pxZbFTgxivIgUnh]{Intelligent Nanites} knack, you can treat the chosen skill as though it were a class skill. If it is already a class skill, you can use half your Constitution modifier instead of your normal modifier to use that skill.</p>\n<p>You must have the intelligent nanites knack to select this knack.</p>\n<p><em>If the skill is already a class skill, you must edit the modifier on the Modifiers tab to select the skill, and replace @abilities.int.mod with the appropriate normal ability modifier for that skill.</em></p>"
